âš ï¸ Common Beginner Mistakes

âŒ Writing `onClick={handleClick()}`
âŒ Forgetting `preventDefault()`
âŒ Mutating state directly
âŒ Complex inline functions
âŒ Forgetting to bind `this` (class)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ’¡ Best Practices

âœ” Use separate handler functions
âœ” Keep logic clean
âœ” Use controlled components for forms
âœ” Use arrow functions for parameters
âœ” Keep components simple

